// Semantic direction:
// observerbarhet implements the OpenTelemetry specification for tracing, metrics, and logs.
// spann is a named, timed unit of work with a unique spann_id and optional foreldre_id.
// tracer_start_spann creates a child spann under tracer_gjeldende_spann automatically.
// kontekst_forplantning injects w3c_traceparent into outgoing requests and extracts from incoming.
// baggage carries key-value pairs alongside trace context across service boundaries.
// type_teller is a monotonically increasing counter (e.g. http_requests_total).
// type_måler records a current value that can go up or down (e.g. active_connections).
// type_histogram buckets observations into histogram_grenser (e.g. request duration distribution).
// oppsummering_kvantil computes p50/p95/p99 latency percentiles over a sliding window.
// logg_korrelasjon_id ties log entries to a specific request or transaction.
// logg_spann_id links log entries to their originating trace spann.
// hale_basert_sampling buffers complete traces in hale_buffer and samples by outcome (e.g. keep errors).
// ressurs_attributt describes the emitting process: service name, version, host, etc.
// batch_eksportør accumulates signals and sends them in batches to reduce network overhead.
// eksport_slipper drops data when the eksport_kø is full, preventing back-pressure cascades.
// probe_livhet returns failure if the process is stuck and should be restarted.
// probe_beredskap returns failure if the process is not yet ready to serve traffic.
// avhengighets_probe checks downstream services (DB, cache) and reports their health.

// Primitive flow:
// innkommende HTTP forespørsel: ekstraher w3c_traceparent
//   tracer_start_spann("http.server", foreldre=ekstrahert_kontekst)
//   spann_attributt({url, metode, status}) -> kjør handler
//   hendelse ved feil: spann_hendelse_obs("feil", {melding})
//   spann_slutt -> eksport via otlp
// metrikk: http_latens = histogram_observer(varighet)
//   per forespørsel: histogram_observer(elapsed_ms) -> oppdater grenser-bøtter
//   prometheus scrape: metrikk_register.serialiser -> eksportør_prometheus
// logg: logg_post(nivå_info, "Behandler forespørsel", {bruker_id, spann_id})
//   -> strukturér som JSON med tjeneste/versjon/miljø-felt -> eksportør_loki
// hale_basert: fullfør spann -> hale_buffer.lagre(spor)
//   ved feil-status: sampler_alltid -> flush spor til eksportør
//   suksess: sampler_sannsynlighet(0.01) -> beholder 1% av vellykkede spor

// This defines observability: OpenTelemetry tracing with context propagation, counters/
// histograms/gauges, structured correlated logging, tail-based sampling, and health probes.
